00:12:16.155 --> 00:12:17.820
because I had a question.

325
00:12:17.820 --> 00:12:19.804
I was reading up to eight hours a day,

326
00:12:19.804 --> 00:12:22.022
this was a, "I've got to get clear on this."

327
00:12:22.022 --> 00:12:24.380
And that is not on a doctrinal level,

328
00:12:24.380 --> 00:12:26.171
the institutional level, the political level.

329
00:12:26.171 --> 00:12:28.219
World religions differ all over the place,

330
00:12:28.219 --> 00:12:30.374
in very significant ways, but when we go to

331
00:12:30.374 --> 00:12:32.464
the depths of contemplative insight,

332
00:12:32.464 --> 00:12:34.331
in the Christian, the Buddhist, and so on,

333
00:12:34.331 --> 00:12:36.613
do they converge, or do they diverge,

334
00:12:36.613 --> 00:12:38.928
