335
00:12:38.928 --> 00:12:41.018
Like, I don't know, fish and apricots.

336
00:12:41.018 --> 00:12:42.842
Just there, you know?

337
00:12:42.842 --> 00:12:45.712
Because I felt that was almost like a geometrical design.

338
00:12:45.712 --> 00:12:47.097
Are they going like this,

339
00:12:47.097 --> 00:12:48.153
are they going like this,

340
00:12:48.153 --> 00:12:49.594
or are they just going like this?

341
00:12:49.594 --> 00:12:53.796
I felt if they diverge, or are just unrelated to each other,

342
00:12:53.796 --> 00:12:57.391
then why should I give credence to any of them?

343
00:12:57.391 --> 00:12:59.929
They're probably just, meditation is probably just

344
00:12:59.929 --> 00:13:03.524
a way of brainwashing yourself to believe or to experience

