00:13:03.524 --> 00:13:06.798
what you've already taught yourself to believe.

346
00:13:06.798 --> 00:13:08.205
In which case, who cares?

347
00:13:08.205 --> 00:13:09.689
I'll find something else to do.

348
00:13:09.689 --> 00:13:11.630
