00:13:15.491 --> 00:13:18.051
and going to an immediacy of experience

352
00:13:18.051 --> 00:13:20.151
that transcends concepts, words, and so forth,

353
00:13:20.151 --> 00:13:22.872
if there appeared to be a profound convergence there,

354
00:13:22.872 --> 00:13:26.648
then my big hunch, that I was willing to bet my life on,

355
00:13:26.648 --> 00:13:29.517
was they're probably converging on the most important truths

356
00:13:29.517 --> 00:13:32.034
human beings have ever encountered.

357
00:13:32.034 --> 00:13:34.082
And that's worth devoting a whole life to.

358
00:13:34.082 --> 00:13:36.236
After a year of study, reading voraciously,

359
00:13:36.236 --> 00:13:37.538
thinking, meditating,

