00:13:41.537 --> 00:13:43.511
this is going to be my working hypothesis:

363
00:13:43.511 --> 00:13:45.356
there's a profound convergence here.

364
00:13:45.356 --> 00:13:46.636
These are the most important truths

365
00:13:46.636 --> 00:13:49.665
we can ever access, and this is all I want to do.

366
00:13:49.665 --> 00:13:52.065
And a place to go now, since I knew my path

367
00:13:52.065 --> 00:13:53.462
was Tibetan Buddhism.

