00:40:09.212 --> 00:40:11.387
So there it is, that's core to the Abrahamic religions,

1080
00:40:11.387 --> 00:40:12.731
all of them.

1081
00:40:12.731 --> 00:40:15.067
Buddhism doesn't even start there, and never goes there.

