00:41:55.425 --> 00:41:57.537
But, by the way, you never see God, right?

1128
00:41:57.537 --> 00:41:59.169
This is everything boils down to matter,

1129
00:41:59.169 --> 00:42:01.035
except, by the way, you never see matter,

1130
00:42:01.035 --> 00:42:02.784
because all you ever see are the data

