1133
00:42:08.816 --> 00:42:11.462
It has to be in terms of your own first person experience,

1134
00:42:11.462 --> 00:42:13.669
and first person experience is not material.

1135
00:42:13.669 --> 00:42:16.314
So it's really quite wonderful, you know,

1136
00:42:16.314 --> 00:42:18.287
that what they believe in so passionately

1137
00:42:18.287 --> 00:42:20.271
is as invisible to them as God is

1138
00:42:20.271 --> 00:42:21.978
to the devout religious believer.

1139
00:42:21.978 --> 00:42:25.007
And Buddhism says neither the twixt nor the twain.

1140
00:42:25.007 --> 00:42:27.450
We're not gonna load the whole burden of reality

