00:42:27.450 --> 00:42:28.825
on some invisible God.

1142
00:42:28.825 --> 00:42:31.407
Nor will we load the whole burden of reality

1143
00:42:31.407 --> 00:42:33.486
on some invisible physical world,

1144
00:42:33.486 --> 00:42:35.395
by the way, we define physical,

1145
00:42:35.395 --> 00:42:37.582
but rather, just come back to experience.

1146
00:42:37.582 --> 00:42:39.129
It's called, in German, the Lebenswelt,

1147
00:42:39.129 --> 00:42:42.425
the world of lived experience, the lived world.

1148
00:42:42.425 --> 00:42:44.942
And there we are, and it doesn't boil down

1149
00:42:44.942 --> 00:42:46.403
to any one category.

