00:42:49.080 --> 00:42:50.712
A kneecap is not made out of mind.

1153
00:42:50.712 --> 00:42:52.696
Clearly there are molecules there,

1154
00:42:52.696 --> 00:42:54.328
but to say, "It's only molecules,"

