1184
00:43:52.532 --> 00:43:55.017
and I think dogmatists,

1185
00:43:55.017 --> 00:43:56.500
whether they're materialistic dogmatists

1186
00:43:56.500 --> 00:43:57.823
or religious dogmatists,

1187
00:43:57.823 --> 00:44:00.542
those people who are just absolutely confident they're right

1188
00:44:00.542 --> 00:44:03.753
and just can't even imagine that they're not.

