00:44:20.861 --> 00:44:23.826
I think this is simply a character type,

1197
00:44:23.826 --> 00:44:25.330
a personality type.

1198
00:44:25.330 --> 00:44:27.197
An intolerance for ambiguity,

1199
00:44:27.197 --> 00:44:29.223
an intolerance for uncertainty,

1200
00:44:29.223 --> 00:44:33.191
and I think I have a rather large tolerance for that,

