00:44:33.191 --> 00:44:35.740
because I like it, because that keeps me active,

1202
00:44:35.740 --> 00:44:38.097
keeps me questing, keeps me want to engage,

1203
00:44:38.097 --> 00:44:40.017
and keeps me wanting to go-

