00:44:42.321 --> 00:44:44.699
it keeps me wanting to go back to the laboratory

1207
00:44:44.699 --> 00:44:46.971
of my meditation hut and explore it,

1208
00:44:46.971 --> 00:44:50.363
come back, not to you just brainwash myself

