1214
00:45:02.149 --> 00:45:03.568
trying to explore as well as I can,

1215
00:45:03.568 --> 00:45:05.178
understand the nature of consciousness,

1216
00:45:05.178 --> 00:45:09.498
and inspired by and based upon experiences,

1217
00:45:09.498 --> 00:45:11.653
I have some pretty strong convictions now.

1218
00:45:11.653 --> 00:45:13.061
