1222
00:45:18.628 --> 00:45:21.124
"We all agree, why don't you?"

1223
00:45:21.124 --> 00:45:22.383
I say, "Well, I know you all agree,

1224
00:45:22.383 --> 00:45:23.908
"but then people have agreed on all kinds of

1225
00:45:23.908 --> 00:45:26.222
"mistaken notions over the years.

1226
00:45:26.222 --> 00:45:28.601
"Show me the empirical evidence."

1227
00:45:30.241 --> 00:45:32.119
If we want to understand something,

1228
00:45:32.119 --> 00:45:34.860
observe it carefully, and don't just observe things

