00:45:47.830 --> 00:45:49.675
Cognitive science is a marvellous science,

1235
00:45:49.675 --> 00:45:50.880
and they're studying things that are

1236
00:45:50.880 --> 00:45:52.363
correlated with mental events,

1237
00:45:52.363 --> 00:45:54.517
but they are not observing mental events directly.

1238
00:45:54.517 --> 00:45:56.629
The only people who are really good at it

1239
00:45:56.629 --> 00:45:59.125
are the ones who, like a neuroscientist has years

1240
00:45:59.125 --> 00:46:00.650
of professional training,

1241
00:46:00.650 --> 00:46:02.869
are people who have years of professional training

1242
00:46:02.869 --> 00:46:05.076
of directly observing the mind.

1243
00:46:05.076 --> 00:46:08.106
And so by the time, if that day comes

1244
00:46:08.106 --> 00:46:11.967
